videos.headline: Ryan Nembhard threads the needle with dime for Gonzaga
videos.description: Ryan Nembhard splits the defense with an incredible pass to Nolan Hickman for a Gonzaga basket down low.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ryan Nembhard threads the needle with dime for Gonzaga) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zags open game with an Anton Watson alley-oop
videos.description: Ryan Nembhard lobs it to Anton Watson for an alley-oop as Gonzaga gets on the board first.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zags open game with an Anton Watson alley-oop) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: San Francisco buries back-to-back triples
videos.description: San Francisco jumps out to a lead over Gonzaga after 3-pointers by Ndewedo Newbury and Marcus Williams.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (San Francisco buries back-to-back triples) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jonathan Mogbo gets the and-1 for the Dons
videos.description: Jonathan Mogbo scores through contact to extend San Francisco's early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jonathan Mogbo gets the and-1 for the Dons) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Braden Huff connects on a hook shot for Gonzaga
videos.description: Braden Huff goes to work in the paint and scores over his defender with a lefty hook shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Braden Huff connects on a hook shot for Gonzaga) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Malik Thomas uses sweet move to score for San Francisco
videos.description: Malik Thomas gets his defender in the air before getting the hoop and the harm vs. Gonzaga.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Malik Thomas uses sweet move to score for San Francisco) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gonzaga storms into the lead with 11-0 run
videos.description: Gonzaga scores 11 straight points late in the first half to take the lead against San Francisco.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gonzaga storms into the lead with 11-0 run) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: San Francisco ends first half with a buzzer-beater
videos.description: Jonathan Mogbo banks in a floater for San Francisco just before the first-half buzzer sounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (San Francisco ends first half with a buzzer-beater) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ben Gregg's 3-ball forces a San Francisco timeout
videos.description: Ben Gregg rattles in a 3-pointer to extend Gonzaga's lead over San Francisco.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ben Gregg's 3-ball forces a San Francisco timeout) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: San Francisco's Marcus Williams T'd up for arguing with refs
videos.description: Marcus Williams argues with the officials about a foul call and is assessed a technical foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (San Francisco's Marcus Williams T'd up for arguing with refs) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ben Gregg heats up with back-to-back treys
videos.description: Gonzaga extends its lead as Ben Gregg connects on a pair of triples within 24 seconds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ben Gregg heats up with back-to-back treys) 2024/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Graham Ike rocks the rim with powerful slam for the Zags
videos.description: Graham Ike throws down an emphatic jam as Gonzaga closes out its victory over San Francisco.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Graham Ike rocks the rim with powerful slam for the Zags) 2024/03/12 ESHEET
